Impressive as the Tesla is I know 95% of people here would still take the Lamborghini.

People also forget this isn't a Chevy Bolt (a very brisk car also), it's every bit as performance orientated as the Lamborghini is where power and traction are concerned.

Would we be as impressed with the Lamborghini going this fast if was also electric? I doubt it.
